{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PCVR enhancements</h2><br>There are several enhancements in the PCVR version compared to the one known from Quest.<br>It's worth mentioning, for example:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>better graphics, <br></li><li>higher resolution, <br></li><li>dynamic lighting, <br></li><li>new and additional VFX, <br></li><li>as well as more environmental elements.</li></ul>Our entire team has made good use of this time to squeeze even more out of Mixture and provide the best entertainment possible!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the game</h2><br>Mixture is a fantasy action-adventure in which two enemies in an alliance of necessity traverse barren worlds in a quest for redemption. In this dual character control game, you alternate between playing as the master alchemist Sephairos and exiled knight Sola, in both first and third person perspectives. \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83e\udd8b As an odd couple, you must platform, mix materials, cast and melee, solve puzzles, and defeat giant bosses to survive this atmospheric tale!<br><br>Mixtures main features:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mix and Slash  \ud83e\uddea\u26cf\ufe0f  </h2>Action adventure gameplay combining the two characters unique skills<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/01_MixAndSLashSHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dual character control \ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83e\udd8b  </h2>Control both the Alchemist Sephairos and the Steel Moth Knight Sola <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/02_DualCharacterSHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the Wastelands  \ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f  </h2>Journey through hand crafted dangerous barren lands of living metals, ores and crystals <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/03_ExploreTheWastelandsSHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight for the light  \u2728 </h2>Oversized bosses to defeat on your path of redemption<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/04_FightForTheLightSHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hours of exploration  \u23f3\ud83c\udf0e </h2>Four unique biomes and more than 30 levels<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/05_Exploration_World__Wilds_SHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An action adventure for standalone VR  \ud83e\udd7d  </h2>Hybrid third person camera and fixed camera movement for hours of comfortable exploration in the Wastelands.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133890/extras/06_ActionAdventureSHORT.gif?t=1726651536\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WISHLIST NOW! \u2705</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Golem Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/3273f78332c8f4a1519345850edb7e0320f7e02c.jpg"},{"name":"Seen it all!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/3cb01d9f0ee0c8887ce301960b18b1a310a7dba5.jpg"},{"name":"First Purchase","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/1aad15adc4285ad59bc8a96820488e522d50f49e.jpg"},{"name":"Lightseed Hoarder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/c1cb7dbe8bbd64db5be67ab7132371e3f0d2bdd4.jpg"},{"name":"Owl-some Rescue","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/0cb9ec3ebb65a74b78fcf36752bef348d4b2c0bd.jpg"},{"name":"Exiled Moth Story","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2133890/f70b2c09574696ba0c965ee5468384ca09a3437a.jpg"},{"name":"Beaten Ram","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com